    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aggregate that consists of gravel, fragments of broken stone, slag, and other coarse substances added to mortar, stucco, or concrete to add strength and stability as well as minimize shrinkage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
